  <objectives>
        <ul>
             <li>   <p>
                 I can describe how a row operation affects the determinant of a matrix.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>   <p>
                I can compute the determinant of a <m>4 \times 4</m> matrix.
                </p>
            </li>
             <li>   <p>
                I can find the eigenvalues of a <m>2 \times 2</m> matrix.
                </p></li>
                <li>   <p>
                I can find a basis for the eigenspace of a <m>4 \times 4</m> matrix associated with a given eigenvalue.
                </p></li>
             <li>   <p>
                I can write <m>A\vvec</m> as a linear combination of eigenvectors.
                </p>
            </li>
            
        </ul>
    </objectives>

